metadata.description: Milo Algandros, Gardener of Eris and Caretaker of the Orchard, is pleased to announce that after millennia of winter, the Golden Orchard of Eris is in full bloom! All who wish to may take a walk among the boughs, feel the grass between their toes, and pick themselves an apple. Remember, each golden apple corps is home to a golden worm!
metadata.name: The 13th
